            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is almost cooked through, add your <strong>ground coriander </strong>to the pan with a pinch<strong> </strong>of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 3-4 min further or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>coriander chicken</strong></p><p>Note: Please make sure you cook your chicken thoroughly (until piping hot) as cooking equipment varies</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1581516215620-x200.jpg",
