            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1625829590742-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> coriander chicken</strong> over the <strong>couscous </strong>and top with the<strong> cucumber batons</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>mint yoghurt</strong></p><p>Garnish with your<strong> flaked almonds</strong>,<strong> remaining chopped mint</strong>,<strong> </strong>a <strong>lemon wedge </strong>and a grind of<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
